Medical Biochemistry - An Illustrated Review - for success in the classroom and on the USMLE!

High-yield, biochemical principles presented in a concise, easy-to-understand format with supporting summary tables
200+ full-color illustrations of biochemical pathways that highlight associated disorders and drug targets
400+ color-coded boxes that connect biochemical concepts with other basic sciences and clinical conditions
400 factual and USMLE-style questions with full explanations online
